Ebbro 43346 Toyota Supra (JZA80) 2002 JGTC Series GT500 Class 7th Place T. Tsuchiya/W. Gardner

Purchased: 2014
Manufacturer page: http://www.ebbro.jp/SHOP/43346.html

Takeshi Tsuchiya & Wayne Gardner raced for triple a Toyota Team TOM's in the 2002 JGTC Series. Their best result was a 2nd place finish in round 4 at Sepang Circuit. They finished 7th overall for the season.

I should have looked at the eBay listing pictures closer as this model is in pretty rough shape. The paint is coming off the wheels and the overall decal/paint finish is not too good.
